%% Trainer Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.2/trainer.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS (self-signed)
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller Manager
    participant Runtime as ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>(cached)
    participant JobSetAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>(JobSet CRUD)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation and Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate TrainJob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob Created

    Note over Controller: Watch event triggers reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime Template

    Controller->>Controller: Build JobSet from Runtime Template<br/>(JobSet Plugin + Torch/MPI Plugin)

    Controller->>JobSetAPI: CREATE/APPLY JobSet<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    JobSetAPI-->>Controller: JobSet Created

    JobSetCtrl->>JobSetCtrl: Reconcile JobSet<br/>Creates Jobs & Pods

    Controller->>K8sAPI: UPDATE TrainJob status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking (RHOAI-specific)

    loop Every 30s (configurable 5s-300s)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (for TrainJob)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list with IPs

        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Progress JSON<br/>(percentage, steps, epochs)

        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>trainer.opendatahub.io/trainerStatus<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 3: Metrics Scraping

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)<br/>insecureSkipVerify
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics

    Note over TrainingPod: Inter-Pod Communication (Training)
    Note over TrainingPod: PyTorch: torchrun rendezvous 29500/TCP
    Note over TrainingPod: MPI: SSH communication 22/TCP
